Examples and tests for pygtk_image.

pygtk_image_test.py  -  Two images are show after one another.

pygtk_image_test2.py -  Images are capture using camera. And shown after
                        a small interval. A req square is drawn, whenever
                        mouse is clicked.
                        
pygtk_mul_image_test.py - Two images are shown simultaneously.
                        
